        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>National Climate Service Corps and Careers Network Act of </b> <b>2021</b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Climate Resiliency Service Corps as a national service program to assist communities in mitigating the effects climate change and establishes the Climate Careers Network to connect individuals with jobs in green industries.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
